OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FA humpback whale known as Timmy has
OL,8,Fbeen confirmed dead by Danish
OL,9,Fauthorities, just two weeks after a
OL,10,Frescue mission when he repeatedly
OL,11,Fbecame stranded off Germany's Baltic
OL,12,FSea coast.
OL,14,FThe dead whale was found on Thursday
OL,15,Fjust off the small island of Anholt in
OL,16,Fthe Kattegat, the broad strait between
OL,17,FDenmark and Sweden that connects the
OL,18,FBaltic Sea to the North Sea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FThe site is about 45 miles away from
OL,8,FSkagen, on the northern tip of
OL,9,FDenmark, where the whale was released
OL,10,Fon May 2 after being transported to
OL,11,Fthe North Sea by barge.
OL,13,F"It can now be confirmed that the
OL,14,Fstranded humpback whale near Anholt is
OL,15,Fthe same whale that was previously
OL,16,Fstranded in Germany and was the
OL,17,Fsubject of rescue attempts," Jane
OL,18,FHansen, head of division at the Danish
OL,19,FEnvironmental Protection Agency, said
OL,20,Fin an emailed statement.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FShe added that conditions on Saturday
OL,8,Fmade it possible for a Danish Nature
OL,9,FAgency employee to locate and retrieve
OL,10,Fa tracking device that was still
OL,11,Ffastened to the whale's back, and "the
OL,12,Fposition and appearance of the device
OL,13,Fconfirm that this is the same whale
OL,14,Fthat had previously been observed and
OL,15,Fhandled in German waters."
OL,17,FThe finding brought a sad end to weeks
OL,18,Fof efforts to guide the mammal back to
OL,19,Fits natural habitat in the Atlantic
OL,20,FOcean.
OL,26,@sD@cOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
