PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FThe whale was first spotted off the
OL,8,FGerman coast on March 3. It's not
OL,9,Fclear why it swam into the Baltic Sea,
OL,10,Fwhich is far from its habitat, and it
OL,11,Fwasn't suited to it, although some
OL,12,Fexperts said it may have lost its way
OL,13,Fwhile swimming after a shoal of
OL,14,Fherring or during migration.
OL,16,FIn late March, it was rescued from
OL,17,Fshallow water in the German Baltic
OL,18,Fresort town of Timmendorfer Strand
OL,19,Fwith the help of an excavator, but it
OL,20,Fsoon ran into trouble again nearby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FLocal media produced days-long
OL,8,Flivestreams, and news sites alerted
OL,9,Freaders to the smallest developments
OL,10,Fin the whale's situation.
OL,12,FAt the beginning of April, experts
OL,13,Fsaid that they had given up hope for
OL,14,Fthe whale and expected it to die in
OL,15,Fthe inlet where it was stranded at the
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
