FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FBut the whale's deteriorating
OL,8,Fcondition prompted a controversy that
OL,9,Fdrew in privately funded rescuers,
OL,10,Fregional authorities and the
OL,11,Fscientific community.
OL,13,FActivists staged protests calling for
OL,14,Fthe animal's rescue, while influencers
OL,15,Fdebated the best way to help it.
OL,17,FSome scientists said that further
OL,18,Frescue efforts would in themselves
OL,19,Fcause the ailing and exhausted animal
OL,20,Fsevere stress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
