PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FThe regional government in Germany's
OL,8,FMecklenburg-Western Pomerania state
OL,9,Fallowed a private rescue initiative to
OL,10,Fgo ahead with the ambitious effort to
OL,11,Fpull the whale onto a flooded barge.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FIt has now been confirmed that the
OL,8,Fnumber tracking device found on the
OL,9,Fdead animal matched the one that had
OL,10,Fbeen attached to the whale. The
OL,11,Finitiative noted that it wasn't
OL,12,Fpossible to say conclusively what
OL,13,Fcaused the whale's death.
OL,15,FMecklenburg-Western Pomerania's
OL,16,Fenvironment minister, Till Backhaus,
OL,17,Fsaid on Saturday that the effort had
OL,18,Fgiven the whale "a last chance to
OL,19,Frecover its freedom and health," but
OL,20,Fit hadn't been able to take that
OL,21,Fchance.
OL,26,@zD@QOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779214266
OL,3,CTimmy the humpback whale found dead on
OL,4,CDanish island weeks after being
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FHe said that it will be important to
OL,8,Flearn "the best possible lessons" from
OL,9,Fthe episode.
OL,11,FBackhaus stressed in a statement that
OL,12,F"acquiescing to the rescue attempt
OL,13,Fdoesn't constitute criticism of
OL,14,Fscience" and added: "I think it is
OL,15,Fabsolutely human to use even the
OL,16,Fsmallest chance when a life is at
OL,17,Fstake."
OL,19,FAuthorities are yet to decide what
OL,20,Fwill be done with the dead whale.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@aO]tD@AOUvD@HO]vD@UOUyD@GO]
